                <td bgcolor="#e9e9e9" valign="top"
 nowrap><b><font color="#000000" face="arial" size="2">Xenoce</font></b></td>
                <td bgcolor="#e9e9e9" valign="top"><font color="#000000" face="arial" size="2"><small>Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;07/20/2003&nbsp;: 10:52:21 PM</small><hr size="2"><span class="spnMessageText"> Have you tried the monolith (sp) next to EC? It is a good camp, plenty of bone chips, and weapons that sell for silver, sometimes gold. Occasionally you get a cracked staff, which sells for about 1pp. Use Numb the dead on every spawn, then pull, and let your pet tank while you cast, when the pets down, step in, cast LT if you can, but when you're almost dead, step back, (the pet should've regened by this point) and chain a few LT's. Rinse, repeat.</span></font></td>
